class.name: CATIAerospaceSheetMetalFactory
class.abstract: Interface to create Aerospace Sheet Metal Features.

method.name: CreateJoggle
method.abstract: Role: This method creates a Joggle Feature.

method.name: CreateSurfacicFlange
method.abstract: Role: This method creates a Surfacic Flange Feature.

method.name: CreateWeb
method.abstract: Role: This method creates a Web Feature.

class.name: CATIStmCharacteristicCurves
class.abstract: Interface to retrieve an aerospace sheet metal characteristic curve body.

method.name: GetAvailableCharacteristicCurveTypes
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves all the characteristic curve types available for this feature.

method.name: GetCharacteristicCurve
method.abstract: Retrieves a characteristic curve associated to <tt>this</tt> feature.

class.name: CATIStmFlangeSurf
class.abstract: Interface to manage the aerospace sheet metal surfacic flange feature.

method.name: GetBaseFeature
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the base feature of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetBaseFeatureOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the base feature orientation of the Surfacic Flange, it defines the base feature side to keep compared to the flange support orientation.

method.name: GetBendRadiusType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the bend radius type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetBendRadiusValue
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the bend radius value of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetEOPElements
method.abstract: Role: This methode retrieves the list of elements of the edge of part if the edge of part type is equal to Element FD or Element FP.

method.name: GetEOPLength
method.abstract: Role: This methode retrieves the length of the edge of part of the surfacic flange if the edge of part type is equal to Length from OML.

method.name: GetEOPType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the edge of part type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetFlangeOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the flange orientation of the Surfacic Flange, it defines the fillet orientation compared to the base feature support orientation.

method.name: GetJoggleCompensation
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves if the joggle compensation is set on the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetJoggles
method.abstract: Role: This methode retrieves the list of joggles of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetKFactor
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the K_Factor associated to the fillet of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetManufacturingProcessType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the manufacturing process type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetMaterialOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the material orientation of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSide1CompensationType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the first side compensation of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSide1CompensationValue
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the first side compensation value of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSide1CornerRadius
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the first side corner value of the surfacic flange if its DressUp type is equal to Corner.

method.name: GetSide1DressUpType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the first side Dress-Up type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSide1Elements
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the first side elements of the surfacic flange if it's type is equal to Element FD or Element FD.

method.name: GetSide1Type
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the first side type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSide2CompensationType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the second side compensation of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSide2CompensationValue
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the second side compensation value of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSide2CornerRadius
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the second side corner value of the surfacic flange if its Dress-Up type is equal to Corner.

method.name: GetSide2DressUpType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the second side Dress-Up type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSide2Elements
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the second side elements of the surfacic flange if it's type is equal to Element FD or Element FD.

method.name: GetSide2Type
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the second side type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSupport
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the support of the surfacic flange.

method.name: GetSupportAngle
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the Angle of the support and the base feature support if Support type is equal to Angle.

method.name: GetSupportApproxLength
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the approximate length of the surfacic flange if Support type is equal to Approximation.

method.name: GetSupportLength
method.abstract: Role: This method is usefull to limit the support of the surfacic flange if the support type is "Angle" or "Exact".

method.name: GetSupportType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the support type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetBaseFeature
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the base feature of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetBaseFeatureOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the base feature orientation of the Surfacic Flange, it defines the base feature side to keep compared to the flange support orientation.

method.name: SetBendRadiusType
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the bend radius type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetEOPElements
method.abstract: Role: This methode sets the list of elements of the edge of part if the edge of part type is equal to Element FD or Element FP.

method.name: SetEOPType
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the edge of part type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetFlangeOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the flange orientation of the Surfacic Flange, it defines the fillet orientation compared to the base feature support orientation.

method.name: SetJoggleCompensation
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the joggle compensation of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetManufacturingProcessType
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the manufacturing process type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetMaterialOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the material orientation of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSide1CompensationType
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the first side compensation of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSide1CompensationValue
method.abstract: Role: This method valuate the first side compensation value of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSide1DressUpType
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the first side Dress-Up type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSide1Elements
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the first side elements of the surfacic flange if it's type is equal to Element FD or Element FD.

method.name: SetSide1Type
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the first side type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSide2CompensationType
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the second side compensation of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSide2CompensationValue
method.abstract: Role: This method valuate the second side compensation value of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSide2DressUpType
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the second side Dress-Up type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSide2Elements
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the second side elements of the surfacic flange if it's type is equal to Element FD or Element FD.

method.name: SetSide2Type
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the second side type of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSupport
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the support of the surfacic flange.

method.name: SetSupportType
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the support type of the surfacic flange.

class.name: CATIStmJoggle
class.abstract: Interface to manage the aerospace sheet metal joggle feature.

method.name: GetClearance
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the clearance length of the Joggle.

method.name: GetDepth
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the depth length parameter of to the joggle.

method.name: GetDepthOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the relative orientation of the depth compared to the joggle support.

method.name: GetEndRadius
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the radius of the end fillet of the Joggle.

method.name: GetPlane
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the start plane of the joggle.

method.name: GetRunout
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the runout length parameter of the joggle.

method.name: GetRunoutOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the relative orientation of the runout compared to the joggle plane.

method.name: GetRunoutType
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the runout definition type of the joggle.

method.name: GetStartRadius
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the radius of the start fillet of the Joggle.

method.name: GetSupport
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the support of the joggle.

method.name: ManageOnSupport
method.abstract: Role: Method to manage Joggle internal specifications.

method.name: SetDepthOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the relative orientation of the depth compared to the joggle support.

method.name: SetPlane
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the start plane of the joggle.

method.name: SetRunoutOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the relative orientation of the runout compared to the joggle plane.

method.name: SetSupport
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the support of the joggle.

class.name: CATIStmWeb
class.abstract: Interface to manage the aerospace sheet metal web feature.

method.name: GetBoundaryElements
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the web boundary limit(s).

method.name: GetJoggles
method.abstract: Role: This methode retrieves the list of joggles of web.

method.name: GetMaterialOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the web material orientation.

method.name: GetSupport
method.abstract: Role: This method retrieves the web support (designed in folded view).

method.name: SetBoundaryElements
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the web boundary limit(s).

method.name: SetMaterialOrient
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the web material orientation.

method.name: SetSupport
method.abstract: Role: This method sets the web support (designed in folded view).
